Package io.openems.edge.core.appmanager.jsonrpc

Class GetAppInstances

java.lang.Object
io.openems.edge.core.appmanager.jsonrpc.GetAppInstances
All Implemented Interfaces:
EndpointRequestType<GetAppInstances.Request,GetAppInstances.Response>
public class GetAppInstances extends Object implements EndpointRequestType<GetAppInstances.Request,GetAppInstances.Response>
Gets the active instances of an OpenemsApp.

Request: 

 {
   "jsonrpc": "2.0",
   "id": "UUID",
   "method": "getAppInstances",
   "params": {
        "appId": string
   }
 }

Response: 

 {
   "jsonrpc": "2.0",
   "id": "UUID",
   "result": {
     "instances": OpenemsAppInstance.toJsonObject()[]
   }
 }
